{"url": "https://www.channel24.co.za/Gossip/News/priyanka-chopra-on-her-hopes-for-meghan-markles-life-as-a-royal-20180503-2", "text": "Cape Town \u2013 Priyanka Chopra has elaborated on her friendship with future royal, Meghan Markle.\n\nThe Quantico actress recently confirmed that she will be attending the royal wedding, set to take place on Saturday, 19 May at St George's Chapel at Windsor Castle.\n\nAnd while she briefly opened up about her relationship with the American actress in an interview with Harper's Bazaar Arabia magazine in February, Priyanka is sharing more about what she thinks of Meghan\u2019s next chapter in life.\n\nDuring an interview on The Jenny McCarthy Show on Wednesday, the Baywatch actress gushed about Meghan saying that she was \u201cborn to be a global influencer\u201d.\n\nPriyanka told Jenny: \u201cShe's always been someone who's so just aware and interested in the world. I met her three or four years ago and that's what we bonded on\u2014was how much we feel like we contribute to that as public people.\n\n\u201cI really feel like that's what she was born to do and I hope this gives her the opportunity do that.\u201d\n\nResponding to a comment that Meghan has received \u201cflak\u201d since her relationship with Prince Harry became public, Priyanka summed up her feelings about it perfectly.\n\n\u201cSome people always talk crap. Haters gonna hate, potatoes gonna potate\u2026Who cares? You do what you do!\u201d\n\nWATCH THE FULL INTERVIEW HERE:\n\n(Forward to 4:43 to hear Priyanka\u2019s kind words about Meghan)", "images": ["https://www.channel24.co.za/images/icons/share/Twitter.svg", "https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/General/d/7347/7978590d8e9449228b8aaa38f57e6ebf.jpg", "https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/General/d/9596/613c56a345a34b9b975f295353467c59.jpg", "https://www.channel24.co.za/images/icons/share/black/instagram.svg", "https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/General/d/3975/c3de66e747f94c45a15f846e3c1f1650.svg", "https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/